  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201601/5f517aa6-65ed-4572-bb32-6efe42f362be.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; width: 500px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; height: 608px; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\" /><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tSuit<br />\n\tTo suit means to make something appropriate for a situation. What is suiting? Why is it suiting? What are the reactions of the people?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They searched for a suiting outfit... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) to suit oneself<br />\n\t2) suiting arrangement<br />\n\t3) follow suit<br />\n\t4) a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fancy\" target=\"_blank\">fancy</a> suit<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe interior designer turned around from where he was sitting and looked again at the two art pieces. The painting hanging on the wall and the sculpture sitting next to the coffee table were rather different. The two art pieces were not contrasting, but they belonged in different genres, each with its own theme and color scheme. The interior designer tried to generalize in his head the type of art work which would suit the club manager's taste. At the moment, however, nothing came to mind. As the club manager walked him out of the office, the designer kept his smile.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166988698488/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768172/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768172\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769290/\">《太阳的后裔》 大热时：撩妹撩汉英文咋说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769555/\">跟我是歌手学英文：See You Again</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2p